# Secret files tracked by the envsecrets CLI (push/pull to GCS) — never committed.
# The "# envsecrets" line below starts the marker section the CLI reads; keep the
# paths directly under it with no blank line or other comment in between. See
# docs/android-release.md.
# envsecrets
android/key.properties
android/app/upload-keystore.jks
